Knights of Solamnia:
--------------------
Occupational:   Set bit (Krynn,1,0)
                Run this command:
exec clone_object("/d/Krynn/solamn/vin/knight/obj/occ_shadow")->shadow_me(find_living(<name>),"occupational","fighter","Solamnian Knights");

exec clone_object("/d/Krynn/solamn/vin/knight/obj/medal")->move(find_living(<name>));
Call <name> add_cmdsoul /d/Krynn/solamn/vin/knight/obj/solamnian_soul
Call <name> update_hooks

The special skills are the following:
- prestige:  108111   (Call <name> change_prestige <num>%%1)
- rescue:    67530
- kattack:   67531
- block:     67532

Occupational only:   Set which order the knight should be in:
Crown:       Call <name> set_knight_level 3               
Sword:       Set bit (Krynn,1,9)    - sword quest must be solved
             Call <name> set_knight_level 4
Rose:        Set bit (Krynn,1,10)   - rose quest must be solved
             Call <name> set_knight_level 5
